<h1>Average upslope flowpath length</h1>

<p>This tool calculates the average length of the flowpaths that run through
each grid cell (in map horizontal units) in a flow pointer grid. The user must
specify the name of a flow pointer grid derived using the <a
href="FlowPointerD8.html">D8 flow algorithm</a> and the output raster image.
</p>

<p>Three temporary images are created during the operation of this tool. Each
of the temporary images should be automatically deleted upon successful
completion. <b><i>NoData</i></b> valued grid cells in the input pointer image
will be assigned <b><i>NoData</i></b> values in the output image. The output
raster is of the <i>float</i> data type and <i>continuous</i> data scale.</p>
<br>


